    prayer: `Lord, thank You for the glorious end toward which all my shining leads: the eternal city where there shall be no night, where You Yourself are my light, and where I shall reign with You forever and ever. As I close this journey, lift my eyes to this hope. Help me to shine on faithfully through whatever darkness remains, knowing that an eternal day is coming, when I will dwell in the light of Your presence and reign with Christ forever. To You be all glory. In the name of Jesus Christ. Amen.`,
